    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a deep dive in a world full of dwarfs. You will unravel the secrets of the village inhabitants and make plenty of friends along the way. Your patience, problem solving and skill will be tested countless of times when slaying lots of bugs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/b1388189d30cab43de81b146d8ba542c.poster.avif?t=1738568448\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/b1388189d30cab43de81b146d8ba542c.webm?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/b1388189d30cab43de81b146d8ba542c.mp4?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase skills and upgrade your character in order to survive your dreams. Gather trophies and make sure the village is safe and happy. Coins are an important currency and you should value it at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/0c9e74b94a7df40d38b8583ada5c6dad.poster.avif?t=1738568448\" width=800 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/0c9e74b94a7df40d38b8583ada5c6dad.webm?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/0c9e74b94a7df40d38b8583ada5c6dad.mp4?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many bugs you can fight with your new obtained skills and free the city from the imminent danger. There are many enemies variants that you'll the discover in your playthrough that will keep you engaged and increase the fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/ff91560306844be94676d2fb88adfcf3.poster.avif?t=1738568448\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/ff91560306844be94676d2fb88adfcf3.webm?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259990/extras/ff91560306844be94676d2fb88adfcf3.mp4?t=1738568448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
